{
  "texts": [
    "Then preprocessing step is done by removing stop words and punctuation.",
    "Afterward, the word frequency is calculated for each word which later helps to calculate individual sentence weights.",
    "This sentence weight represents the importance of that sentence.",
    "Then the top 10 percent of sentences are selected as the final output.",
    "The model is later evaluated using ROUGE scores to get an overview of the performance."
  ]
}